                android:text="The Department of MBA started functioning in the Year 2006 with two year's MBA course affiliated to GB Technical University, Lucknow with an intake of 60 Students. Committed to impart value based quality management education to the budding professionals, the department has a competent core faculty, which aims to groom its students on necessary competence and skills required for the effective management of today's business. With latest techniques and innovations, the Institute infuses the knowledge of global prospective on various management issues; general management, competencies, decision making abilities and administrative competence; conceptual knowledge on the subject and behavioral skills; entrepreneurial capabilities and business leadership, team building and sensibility for group learning and problem solving, among the students.It offers specialization in Human Resources Management, Finance, Marketing and Information Technology and International Business.The campus always remains abuzz with industrial interactions, seminars and guest lectures on important topics to update students about the current trends of the business world. Beside the syllabus, short term personality development programs are also conducted for the students. The department has a state-of-art Computer lab along with a well stocked integral departmental Library with an extended facility of IIM (Library) membership."
